Program: Outlook
Title: Private Security Firms in Iraq
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsmn
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Ugandan civilian security guards and dog handlers on working in Iraq. Also, Sally Roach, the former midwife who delivered a baby on an aeroplane. Maldives human rights activist Jennifer Latif on being cleared of terrorism charges. Spending a day with a postman in Rajasthan, India. Finally, a Dutch charity is victim of a violent robbery in Kenya. Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less